    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:205px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box2" style="text-align:right;"><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Gearing FB</text> : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Gearing FB</text> modifies motion-values with a linear equation / function. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The function has 3 parameters - see below</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">Gearing FB function</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">The function of the <text styleclass="Element">Gearing FB</text> is:</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="VariableName">Output =</text><text style="font-weight:normal;">&#32;</text><text style="font-size:16pt; font-weight:normal;">(</text><image src="1r.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:8pt; font-weight:normal; vertical-align:sub;" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text style="font-weight:normal;">&#32;</text><text style="font-size:16pt; font-weight:normal;">*</text><text styleclass="VariableName"> (Input + </text><image src="2r.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="VariableName" style="font-size:7pt; vertical-align:sub;" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="VariableName">)) + </text><image src="3r.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="VariableName" style="font-size:7pt; vertical-align:sub;" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">Use the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-FunctionBlock-Gearing" styleclass="Element">Gearing FB dialog</link> to edit the three parameters <image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><image src="Red-14-3.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
